This is a list of [[television program]]s broadcast by [[Sky Living]] in the [[United Kingdom]] and [[Ireland]]. The schedule for Living currently consists of a mixture of American and British comedy, drama and factual programming. The channel is pitched towards a female-targeted audience but has in recent years change that position to include males. The channel also shows commissioned content from other Living TV Group channels as well as its own commissioned content on both Sky Living and Sky Livingit.
